OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FOffer gene test to stroke  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpatients, NHS told         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, People who have had a stroke caused by 
OL,6, a blood clot should have a DNA test to 
OL,7, see whether they can be given a drug to
OL,8, help prevent more brain attacks, new   
OL,9, draft guidelines for the NHS say.      
OL,11,FStroke risk increases when someone has 
OL,12,Fhad one previously, which is why       
OL,13,Fpreventive medication is recommended.  
OL,15,FBut a standard anti-clot drug,         
OL,16,Fclopidogrel, works well for patients   
OL,17,Fwith certain genes only.               
OL,19,FOthers need a different protective drug
OL,20,F- so the gene check could save lives.  
